README

This is a collection of scripts for working with BLAST.

getFastas.pl - a script to pull out a specific set of protein sequences from a .faa file, for use with BLAST
BLASTsplitter.pl - a script to pull out all BLAST matches of a certain minimum bit score from BLAST output
BlastTopHits.pl - a script to pull out the top BLAST hit for each protein query in BLAST output
